{"tid":1626652,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果學校範圍唔算公眾地方 聽日一齊返學校有無得諗","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:28:43.000Z","uid":93451,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"be5e20aab9f02eaa1e4863aa5381e4c9e6d987a4","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人都認為聽日係和理非回合  <br />\n想出去表達 打下條國際線<br />\n但揾唔到一個一開始同最後唔比人清場嘅方法<br />\n但如果我地帶口罩係大學 <br />\n校友\b,大學生,中學生 仲有唔同年齡愛香港嘅香港人<br />\n一齊進行學術討論討論下香港又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹諗到想討論下可行性"},{"pid":"0763e65b077173d322d0c09b7584fb5a4037983b","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"可能時間宣傳係好趕<br />\n但聽日最緊要係做到野 同安全<br />\n最好有法律巴絲入黎分析下"},{"pid":"7414f33a068807ef784ebd16d97330434ec798d1","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"如果八大有好多香港人坐晒係到帶口罩表達自己意見<br />\n我覺得個畫面會同二百萬人一樣咁好睇"},{"pid":"cc374d6cd146d9c90ddb2a77f9bf7e535abbd349","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"x1"},{"pid":"6f82bbc94ebfec2e31f9af18383952d0c2ab466f","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1d604fcd5470e1857bb110a230a4775c78269595","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"如果聽日搞唔切 星期一 星期二<br />\n重點係想傾下可唔可行<br />\n各大學生會其實會唔會搞得到一個咁既活動<br />\n會唔會唔洗申請不反對 又唔會比人搞到"},{"pid":"887d6648721d0e4b11aa69b7a35eec0bc1f16017","tid":1626652,"uid":266503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"返學校集會"},{"pid":"9ef81ca327b0e97cade84dc2f6093b027c2faeb8","tid":1626652,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52c6b3264604a4db7154354ecd1dc47fdba4f46f","tid":1626652,"ui